In 2014, they began preparing the Shippansee LTD app, which uses to transport packages of already planned journeys between the world's capitals, primarily aircraft.
In 2015, they awarded a project for the processing of a company that created applications for example for MALL.cz, Jobs.cz or ČSFD.
